Package main.java.com.spaceexplorer.model

Enum Class ResourceType

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ResourceType>
main.java.com.spaceexplorer.model.ResourceType
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ResourceType>, Constable
public enum ResourceType extends Enum<ResourceType>
Enumeration of available resource types in the game. Resources can be collected by players from various space objects. Each resource type has a description that provides more detail about the resource.
Since:
1.0
